      <bioghist id="aspace_bioghist">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Samantha L. Lyon, Class of 2008</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_scope">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection contains materials describing the activities of Samantha Lyon including materials from courses and extracurricular activities. Specific material pertaining the founding of Smith College's Bicycle Kitchen and its incorporation with the Student Government Association as well as materials related to Ms. Lyon's "Documenting Oral Histories: Activism at Smith" research thesis. Types of materials include photographs, invitations, newspaper clippings, programs, letters, and DVDs.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
